ale ordered toroidal B-field suggests that a) the infalling gas\nthat fuels RL AGN is magnetized, b) there is a magnetohydrodynamic wind that\ncollimates the jet, and/or c) the jet is able to magnetize its surroundings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 17:48:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 18:01:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-11"}
