hat compared to state-of-the-art methods, our proposed framework\ncan reduce a large amount of model parameter transfer between the cloud server\nand the IoT device while improving the performance by approximately 2.2% when\ndealing with corrupted data. The code is available at\nhttps://github.com/evoxlos/mono-cnn-pytorch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2022 02:00:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 05:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
